name: PayBilis
overview:
Paybilis is a mobile technology company that promotes cashless economy by the means of electronic payments as a method of payment or money transfer.

Paybilis empowers people by letting consumers pay their bills using any mobile device without queuing in payment centers and banks anymore. This is a new way of mobile banking that integrates with your bank accounts and let consumers pay their bills anytime and anywhere they are.

The support doesn’t stop on making an access to this entrepreneur’s to accept payments electronically but also extending hand to lower the bank interchange to a significant percentage.

Paybilis is partnering with the government to help them do efficient collection of payments / accounts receivables. In this way the company is helping the government to lessen or eliminate corruption by providing systems that will help collect payments efficiently the different agencies of the government.
